{"tid":1577611,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"好想做唱片公司既office staff","createTime":"2019-09-17T19:02:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T06:56:16.000Z","uid":140421,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2a83515cd16b93599115bb5e6e38da59a78c9351","tid":1577611,"uid":140421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T19:02:55.000Z","msg":"19fg marketing 上網搵左好多工都覺得無乜動力去報 反而個心一直好想搵到唱片公司既office post 奈何好似全部都要人介紹先入到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁想入唱片公司主要有幾個原因<br />\n一係我係一個好欣賞歌手既人 <br />\n二係 既然翻其他工都要比人問老母 都要ot到無生活 咁我不如搵翻滿足到自己既工 當係公司benefit都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底有咩方法可以入到去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果入到我真係唔介意日日ot<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"491a85691bb3f145678ba26d9349de9f65fd0737","tid":1577611,"uid":16743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:49:20.000Z","msg":"pm me"},{"pid":"942ad0c06fa98ed53927eee77c83f62be57dccc7","tid":1577611,"uid":16743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"491a85691bb3f145678ba26d9349de9f65fd0737","tid":1577611,"uid":16743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:49:20.000Z","msg":"pm me"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:50:46.000Z","msg":"diu sorry on9 tg pls <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96eb8ec126b5f65550d7aa7e32a28771f93c68e1","tid":1577611,"uid":120544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:19:09.000Z","msg":"同你一樣<br />\n一直搵緊呢類工<br />\n但係又唔識人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26f21235493fba2b608fa945754d69ac83abdae3","tid":1577611,"uid":298,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:23:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/